messages.content: What is the purpose of ComfyUI-Depth-Visualization?
ComfyUI-Depth-Visualization is a tool that works with any Depth Map and visualizes the applied version of it inside ComfyUI.
Who is acknowledged in the ComfyUI-Depth-Visualization documentation?
The ComfyUI-Depth-Visualization documentation acknowledges flowtyone for their work on ComfyUI-Flowty-TripoSR.
